%e A225577 a(4)=5 since 1^2,2^2,3^2,4^2 are incongruent modulo 2^5-1=31, but 1^2==4^2 (mod 2^4-1), 3^2==4^2 (mod 2^3-1) and 2^2==4^2 (mod 2^2-1).
